@startuml Auth_AES_Handler_FSM

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor LightGreen
    BorderColor DarkGreen
    FontSize 12
}

title AES Handshake Helper (auth_aes_handler) - FSM

[*] --> IDLE : rst

state IDLE : wait ready
state WRITE_INIT : aes_core_init=1 (pulse)
state READ_READY : wait aes_core_ready
state WRITE_BLOCK : aes_core_next=1 (pulse)
state READ_VALID : wait result_valid\nvalid_o=1 then return

IDLE --> WRITE_INIT : ready
WRITE_INIT --> READ_READY
READ_READY --> WRITE_BLOCK : aes_core_ready
WRITE_BLOCK --> READ_VALID
READ_VALID --> IDLE : result_valid

@enduml
